When you've spent years planning and mapping out your life in stages only for things to not go as planned, can be the hardest and most heartbreaking truth to accept. Unforeseen circumstances, rock bottom lows and even the loss of loved ones will cause us to have to deviate and redirect. Letting go of what once was to now accept what no longer is. But the beautiful thing about life is that all the experiences you go through is creating a stronger more resilient version of you. Now walking into a Grandiose life better than you could have ever envioned. When you simply let go and trust the process all the things you've been wanting finally shows up ✨

#2023goals #selflove❤️ #purposeful #selfgrowthjourney  #trusttheprocess #trustgodswill #faithwalk #believers #godschosen
